<item>
            <title>[HBASE-6425] Change unit for hbase.hregion.majorcompaction to hours</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-6425</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently it needs to be specified in millisecs when it usually is a big duration. It would make more sense to specify it in hours.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12599382">HBASE-6425</key>
            <summary>Change unit for hbase.hregion.majorcompaction to hours</summary>
